Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛有家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個部隊中有妻兒的只有我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的所屬是炮兵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務是把各種人頭般大小的炮彈不斷射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在流落街頭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然來訪亞洲的蔻蔻小姐就雇傭了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸~如同各位手邊的資料所示..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空運！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海克梅迪亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的運送 就全拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德拉貢·尼克拉維奇是民兵組織「巴爾幹之龍」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡稱「巴龍」組織的頭目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳是不是在那架運輸機裏藏了十個混球醫生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我老實交代！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 又冒出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又冒出來一堆黑帽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:01:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的存在變成了海克梅迪亞小姐的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再繼續裝貨物下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療我打傷的“敵人”的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話你也是敵人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔻蔻 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此也沒有其他辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把民兵「巴爾幹之龍」殲滅掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好近！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好近！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍..槍戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.51,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:50.51,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始終踱步於境界線之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:53.23,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:53.23,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境風景獨好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:55.85,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeny,meeny,miny,moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:55.85,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一，二，三，四...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.79,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,much the same
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.79,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:01.05,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:01.05,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始終踱步於境界線之上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:04.33,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:04.33,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境風景獨好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:24.83,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pike or shield?  負けたくはない　でも傷つけたくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:24.83,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矛 or 盾？ 不想認輸 可是又不願受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.82,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手に取って　確かめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.82,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先挑一樣在手中仔細掂量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.02,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと戻れないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.02,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是發現再要反悔為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:35.47,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:35.47,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選的是哪邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.25,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思い出は枷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.25,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思念是枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.77,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  後付けのlove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.77,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  追悔莫及的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.58,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  優しさは仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.58,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  溫柔是弱點
